    u=0.20: Z_P^-1 = 8.388608e-01, Z_I^-1 = 8.333056e-01

  2. CYCLE COUNTS (N_k = #primitive k-cycles)
       k        Tr_P(A^k)        Tr_I(A^k)       N_k(P)       N_k(I)      Delta_N
       3               42               42           14           14            0
       5              210              140           42           28          -14
       7             2226             2765          318          395           77

  3. ODD-CYCLE GRAPH Ω(T)
    Paley: 35 odd cycles
    Interval: 35 odd cycles
      (0, 1, 3)
      (0, 1, 5)
      (0, 2, 3)
      (0, 2, 6)
      (0, 4, 5)
      (0, 4, 6)
      (1, 2, 4)
